::Neody::

A bot stands atop the mountain that Cygnar and Like-Like are near, 
watching the two. He had arrived here seconds before after trying to 
get to the base that he had been assigned to. As he could now clearly 
see, the base was buried under the mountain.

He sets off down the mountain, heading for the two bots at its foot.
